# END-END Testing

## Overview

This directory contains e2e testing scripts for our application.

## Test run by tags

1. npx playwright test --grep @smoke

## Run Single Test case

1. npx playwright test tests/example.spec.ts -g "Test case name"

## Run test case Based on View port

## Run only Admin (Web Only):

1. npx playwright test --project="Admin - Web"

## Run only Business & Patron on Web:

2. npx playwright test --project="Business & Patron - Web"

## Run only Business & Patron on Mobile:

3. npx playwright test --project="Business & Patron - Mobile"

## Run all tests:

4. npx playwright test
